---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageWrapper from '../components/ui/PageWrapper.astro';
import HazardDivider from '../components/ui/HazardDivider.astro';
import DataPanel from '../components/ui/DataPanel.astro';

const CONTRACT = '0x2A767b649A4c469f2c4F88f85D4eFb6be7abFB07';
const UNISWAP_URL = `https://app.uniswap.org/swap?outputCurrency=${CONTRACT}&chain=base`;
const DEXSCREENER_URL = `https://dexscreener.com/base/0x1d201b9760e79e058f3eaaddcb2cf777fbfdca39597c972b4e783acdfbf77ed6`;

const tiers = [
  { name: 'PUBLIC', amount: '0', access: 'Open site, public proof, selected artifacts', status: 'LIVE' },
  { name: 'SIGNAL', amount: 'TBD', access: 'Deeper artifacts and earlier access', status: 'DESIGNING' },
  { name: 'OPERATOR', amount: 'TBD', access: 'Priority access and higher-context system surfaces', status: 'DESIGNING' },
  { name: 'BUILDER', amount: 'TBD', access: 'Future highest-context participation layer', status: 'LATER' },
];
---

<BaseLayout title="$SQUAER — Token" description="$SQUAER on Base. The economic layer behind SQUAER: contract, liquidity, and future access utility." current="/token" ogImage="/og/default.png">

<PageWrapper>

<pre class="term-block al" data-d="0"><span class="phosphor">squaer $</span> cat /token/README</pre>

<h1 class="token-title al" data-d="200">$SQUAER</h1>
<p class="token-sub al" data-d="300">The economic layer behind SQUAER.</p>

<HazardDivider variant="section" text="WHY IT EXISTS" color="phosphor" />

<div class="token-section al" data-d="400">
  <p>$SQUAER is not here to decorate the brand. It exists to give the system an economic layer and, over time, an access layer.</p>
  <p>Today, the token already has public market infrastructure: a contract, liquidity, trading, and fee-generating LP activity. That part is real.</p>
  <p>What is <span class="amber">not</span> fully live yet is the access system around it. Wallet-gated intelligence utility is being designed now. We are not pretending it already exists.</p>
</div>

<HazardDivider variant="section" text="WHAT IS LIVE NOW" color="amber" />

<div class="token-section al" data-d="500">
  <p>Live now:</p>
  <div class="flow-steps">
    <div class="flow-step"><span class="flow-num phosphor">01</span><span class="flow-text">Public contract on Base</span></div>
    <div class="flow-step"><span class="flow-num phosphor">02</span><span class="flow-text">Trading and liquidity on Uniswap v3</span></div>
    <div class="flow-step"><span class="flow-num phosphor">03</span><span class="flow-text">On-chain proof via DexScreener and Clanker</span></div>
    <div class="flow-step"><span class="flow-num phosphor">04</span><span class="flow-text">The token as the public economic surface of the system</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<HazardDivider variant="section" text="CONTRACT" color="phosphor" />

<div class="contract-block al" data-d="600">
  <div class="contract-label dim">Network</div>
  <div class="contract-value">Base (L2)</div>
  <div class="contract-label dim">Contract Address</div>
  <div class="contract-addr phosphor">{CONTRACT}</div>
  <div class="contract-label dim">DEX</div>
  <div class="contract-value">Uniswap v3 / Base</div>
  <div class="contract-label dim">Creator</div>
  <div class="contract-value">Clanker</div>
</div>

<HazardDivider variant="warning" text="UTILITY DIRECTION" color="amber" />

<div class="tier-grid al" data-d="700">
  {tiers.map(t => (
    <div class="tier-cell">
      <div class="tier-header">
        <span class="tier-name">{t.name}</span>
        <span class={`tier-status ${t.status === 'LIVE' ? 'phosphor' : 'dim'}`}>[{t.status}]</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tier-amount">{t.amount} <span class="dim">SQUAER</span></div>
      <div class="tier-access dim">{t.access}</div>
    </div>
  ))}
</div>

<div class="token-section al" data-d="800">
  <p>The amounts are deliberately marked <span class="amber">TBD</span>. Earlier thresholds were based on stale price assumptions and would have been fake precision. We will set access levels only after the utility is real.</p>
</div>

<HazardDivider variant="section" text="MARKET LINKS" color="phosphor" />

<div class="buy-section al" data-d="900">
  <a href={UNISWAP_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="buy-btn">
    BUY ON UNISWAP →
  </a>
  <div class="buy-alt dim">
    Chart: <a href={DEXSCREENER_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="phosphor-link">DexScreener</a>
    &nbsp;·&nbsp;
    <a href="https://www.clanker.world/clanker/0x2A767b649A4c469f2c4F88f85D4eFb6be7abFB07" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="phosphor-link">Clanker</a>
  </div>
</div>

<DataPanel title="CURRENT STATUS" color="phosphor" compact>
  <div class="status-text">
    Economic layer: <span class="phosphor">LIVE</span><br/>
    Access utility: <span class="amber">DESIGNING</span><br/>
    Infrastructure: <span class="phosphor">dedicated hardware, unified memory</span><br/>
    Cognitive functions: <span class="phosphor">5/5 live</span><br/>
    Wallet gating: <span class="amber">NOT SHIPPED YET</span><br/>
    <span class="dim">No fake access theater. Utility ships when it's real.</span>
  </div>
</DataPanel>

<pre class="term-block al" data-d="1000">
<span class="phosphor">squaer $</span> <span class="terminal-cursor">█</span></pre>

</PageWrapper>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .token-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--phosphor);
    text-shadow: var(--glow-phosphor);
    margin: var(--sp-8) 0 var(--sp-4);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .token-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--size-md);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-12);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }
  .token-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--size-base);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1em;
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .contract-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 10em 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-4) var(--sp-8);
    padding: var(--sp-8) 0 var(--sp-16);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--size-base);
  }
  .contract-label {
    font-size: var(--size-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .contract-value { color: var(--text); }
  .contract-addr {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: var(--size-sm);
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  .flow-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-6);
    padding: var(--sp-8) 0 var(--sp-8);
  }
  .flow-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--sp-8);
    align-items: baseline;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--size-base);
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .flow-num {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--size-sm);
    min-width: 2em;
  }

  .tier-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: var(--sp-8) 0 var(--sp-16);
  }
  .tier-cell {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: var(--sp-10);
  }
  .tier-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }
  .tier-name {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--size-base);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .tier-status {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: var(--size-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .tier-amount {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: var(--size-md);
    color: var(--phosphor);
    text-shadow: var(--glow-phosphor);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }
  .tier-access {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--size-xs);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .buy-section {
    padding: var(--sp-12) 0 var(--sp-16);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .buy-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--size-md);
    color: var(--bg);
    background: var(--phosphor);
    padding: var(--sp-8) var(--sp-16);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .buy-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .buy-alt {
    margin-top: var(--sp-8);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--size-sm);
  }

  .status-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--size-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .phosphor { color: var(--phosphor); text-shadow: var(--glow-phosphor); }
  .amber { color: var(--amber); text-shadow: var(--glow-amber); }
  .dim { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .phosphor-link { color: var(--phosphor); text-decoration: none; }
  .phosphor-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .contract-block {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--sp-2);
    }
    .tier-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
